{
  "stem": "9262.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, where we lived, in our courtyard-- it was like a half-moon shape, these houses, these apartment blocks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Some of they're facing the street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Others were facing the interior.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the poor people usually lived down in the basements or on the mezzanine floor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And those who had nothing were usually told by one or two of the neighbors, who were in charge of the welfare of the block, looking who has got nothing, they would stop us and they say, oh, so and so and so has got nothing.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Would you give something?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So people used to buy challah bread for them, or they used to buy a small little fish.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or they would say, well, they can have two pounds of meat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I say two pounds, this is about a kilo.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A kilo is about two and  a half pounds really [INAUDIBLE] weight.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Joe, I'd like to ask you what you remember  about the outbreak of the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We will come to that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that's how life was before the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Regarding health service, people, when they were working in a place in the office or in a factory, like my uncle who was the manufacturer, had to pay for each of the employees' sickness benefit.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the sickness benefit was paid to the government.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So if any of the employees became sick or needed medical attention, they would go to a clinic, which was free because they were in that scheme, in that health service scheme.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think the first time I had to go to one of these clinics was when I came back from my holidays.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This [? actually ?] was 1938.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I went to the clinics.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "All the doctors there were Poles.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
